  <article class="sidebar-content">
    <section class="row section styleguide-section with-copy">
      <h1>Neue Pattern Library</h1>

      <p>This is Neue, our interface framework and pattern library. Neue is made up of four pillars: typography, a fluid grid-based layout system, re-usable interface patterns, and animations. It's a strong foundation for building beautiful interfaces.</p>
    </section>

